{"tid":1946145,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黑警就確診狗女無戴口罩深感抱歉　認為其防疫意識不足","createTime":"2020-03-27T12:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T12:46:21.000Z","uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"869794e678609648bcc2c6906caba1bb395deecb","tid":1946145,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1517293_1_L_20200327195855.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1517293_1_L_20200327195855.jpg&h=4c9c4792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方就一名確診新型肺炎女警，在明愛醫院留醫期間曾部分時間無戴口罩事件，表示深感抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n有關女警在醫院抽血期間無戴口罩，照顧她的兩名抽血員被列為密切接觸者，要隔離檢疫14日，其中一人不適，要到急症室治療。<br />\n<br />\n警方在社交平台就事件表示深感抱歉，又說警方高度關注事件，認為有關警員防疫意識不足，已即時聯絡她了解事件，並要求她必須遵照醫護人員指示，保護他人避免受到感染。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警方就事件對醫護人員及服務構成影響，並引起社會不安，深感抱歉。為避免同類事件發生，警方會提醒全體警務人員，要積極配合醫護人員的防疫工作，應時刻保持個人衞生，減低傳播風險。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517293-20200327.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517293-20200327.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3flmNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=1278eec3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517293-20200327.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d229cd69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517293-20200327.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b59ad19573a4d375bd63cad8eb1d2b86e47a6a3a","tid":1946145,"uid":162456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NpziJe1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNpziJe1.jpg&h=5687ab64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cKHDJe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKHDJ